overview: Naughty America presents volume 23 of every man's fantasy! To have two girls of this ilk would make the strongest man weak! Natasha Nice, Katrina Jade, AJ Applegate, Keisha Grey and Rachael Madori headline the cast!
tagline: A few have done it, some of us have gotten close, all have fantasized about it...2 Chicks Same Time!
title: 2 Chicks Same Time 23
